timing_check_...ort_all_checks(25.10)    timing_check_...ort_all_checks(25.10)

Name
       timing_check_timing_report_all_checks

Syntax
       timing_check_timing_report_all_checks

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables  reporting of all the checks performed by the check_timing com-
       mand.

       When set to true, the check_timing command reports all the checks  per-
       formed,  even  if  there is no violation(s) for the corresponding check
       type.

       When set to false, only the check types that have any  violations  will
       be reported.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

